metadata.name: Artifact #1
metadata.description:
**Artifact #1 minted by "Van Gogh’s Ear"**

*Creator Edition 1/1*

**About**: Hand painted in virtual reality by Nak Yong Choi with original music by Elliot Cole and creative direction by René Pinnell, "Van Gogh's Ear" is the genesis Artifact for the Artizen Fund.

**Impact**: Unlock human creativity

**Team**: [Nak Yong Choi](https://knocknak.com/),  [Elliot Cole](https://twitter.com/elliotcole), [René Pinnell](https://twitter.com/RJPinnell)

Artifact #1 is in the [public domain](https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/).

**Supported by the [Artizen Fund](https://www.artizen.fund/) for human creativity**
